Oromia Will be away for Summer Vacation!

Cheers!

Thanks for the prompt upload.  Tragedy to hear you'll not be uploading during July.  Can only hope someone (anyone?) will fill in.  Can't go without my Economist fix.   Boy, I can hear the girls of the world getting wet.
Ditto Jezza! You got me hooked on the Economist and the New Yorker... so much so I'll be subscribing to both for this coming school year! Hope you have a great vacay Oromia! Thanks again!
Galatoomi/ galatoomaa.All the best in your vacation.Stay blessed!!
